Package Users

Class Student

java.lang.Object
Users.User
Users.Student
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Student extends User
The `Student` class represents a student user in the system. Students have the ability to register for and manage their participation in camps.

      public boolean registerCamp(Camp camp, boolean attendee)
      Registers the student for a camp, either as an attendee or committee member.
      Parameters:
      camp - The camp to be registered for.
      attendee - `true` if registering as an attendee, `false` for committee member.
